  "text": "Gastric cancer is one of the leading causes of cancer-related mortality in developed and undeveloped countries [CITATION_1] . The five-year survival rate for patients with gastric cancer is <35%, as the currently available chemotherapeutic regimens are not highly effective. Furthermore, the high recurrence rates and nodal metastasis also require consideration [CITATION_2] .",
